data.description: Welcome home to Stunning views and breathtaking sunsets. This beautifully designed and updated home will capture your attention from the moment you step inside. This is where Santa Fe meets Texas Hill country. Private gate greets you at the end of the cul-de-sac and welcomes you onto the property with a long driveway leading you in.  Double door entry with glass windows give guests a sneak peak of the beautiful hill country view and sky. Inside you will take in all the details of the Adobe Santa Fe inspired design in the living room and dining area with high ceilings, pine beams, and turquoise door accent. Plenty of room for relaxation or entertaining in the oversized living room with built in shelving and fireplace. Large picture windows allow so much natural light and views from morning until sunset. Enjoy cooking in your updated kitchen with built in appliances, plenty of counter space and a window over the sink to take in more natural landscape and trees. Step down into your oversized primary bedroom with large windows showcasing the views in your backyard, shelves for books or art and fall in love with your 2 sides fireplace, cedar closet and huge shower with a double vanity. Laundry room was added inside primary bedroom for convenience. Secondary bedroom down the hall has a great view of the trees and landscape too. Guest suite or use as a secondary primary with it's own living room, full bath and private entry. 2 car oversized garage with a temperature controlled storage room. This home is so unique and offers so much character, detail and truly shows off pride of ownership. Be ready for entertaining and enjoyment of your view with your oversized composite deck that will be sure to be the spot you take in your morning coffee or end the day with a dessert and nightcap. Home sits on 2.56 acres and offers So much privacy and space to feel so far away but yet so close to San Antonio, New Braunfels and Bulverde. Get ready to fall in love with this home in Spring Branch. Great schools and minutes to shopping and dining.
